\"paragraph\"><strong>Implementation exercise</strong></span></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>Run a malformed invoice or missing-PO case and prove the notebook produces a deterministic rejection with the correct reason code.</li>\n</ul></span></div>"
